# Circle Agent Stack
# Authentication is handled by the Circle CLI itself. There is no Circle API
# key. Before the first demo run, complete the one-time host setup (setup.md
# steps 1-2: CLI install, skill install) and accept the Terms of Use. The demo
# logs you in with email + OTP on its first run; see the README "Host setup" and
# "Login" sections. The CLI stores credentials under ~/.circle (override with
# CIRCLE_CLI_HOME).
# https://developers.circle.com/agent-stack
#
# The kit operates on Base mainnet only; there is no chain to configure.

# Claude Agent SDK auth. Required. The kit authenticates with an API key only,
# which keeps the spawned Claude Code subprocess non-interactive (the OAuth /
# subscription path can hang it on a login prompt). Get a key at
# https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional model override (default: claude-sonnet-4-6)
# LLM_MODEL=
